佢哋無錯，而唔會令佢醒覺覺得自己做錯。<br />\n<br />\n即係日劇有時都會見到有一啲殺人犯或者精神有問題嘅人犯案，佢哋去到俾人拉，甚至上到法庭嘅時候，都覺得自己係冇錯嘅。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">警察已經成魔。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要大家繼續不割𥱊，宜家要搞返好PR同形象工程！</span> 暫時忍住唔好放火，雖然我知大家好撚火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會之後，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>機場</strong></span>或者真係安全又簡單嘅地方重新起步，一齊和你飛。<br />\n好耐無去旅行喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> &ldquo;The simplest moves are the best.&rdquo; </span></span></span></strong><br />\n- Napoleon Bonaparte<br />\n<br />\nP牌，第一次出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家留言討論下<br />\n<br />\n不割𥱊，一定要記得我地嘅初心<br />\n守護司法制度同香港的核心價值<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> P.s. 手足唔好再寫錯<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>時<span style=\"font-size: large;\">伐</span>革命</strong></span>喇！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80a908970e3ec1ff1cc81fc202c8242a1782616b","tid":1419582,"uid":38136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"deeecaec372dd08d58432a6afa2b4510b34d6992","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得最少要有個光譜協調返整個行動。<br />\n雖然係<em><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山</span></strong></em>，但目標要一齊爬上山，並唔只係一部分人。<br />\n<br />\n要顧埋後面，幫一幫落後左嘅人上返黎，否則跟唔上嘅人會放棄，咁就好快玩完。"},{"pid":"b74dac01fd4c366b78e4e71a249b5ae3a8943c65","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"bb1aca40e51caa14d0ea7eb027fa3e06bdf46c70","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"291fbd6e08bba548f9ef6891cd365fff796eb47d","tid":1419582,"uid":275471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"細細力推一下"},{"pid":"12a98d036a1fa34b9f15f11ef22538403323fdff","tid":1419582,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"ac58f7f2b83dc4f010126a9fe2ac2781e2e42367","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0294564beebd6bec029a17236b20b090c0bf40d9","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb23a479c8a4e98b3812f5f6da7f96b036a6d45","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5166ad4fcf803576402dc62c411d1eb726d6fa4c","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12f2221f14c8f6262b93dac5e28d0a94d7e7f267","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a15eefe40ad3757c70fa5ced81426402feb6380","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2431376dc91c7592e838971753e0d54330c66e9e","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3b32d13742f1075ff6a1f50e88f46fc1b92ae666","tid":1419582,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"